definitions.definition: To crash ; to have an accident while controlling a vehicle.
definitions.label_groups: intransitive , chiefly Australia and New Zealand , UK , informal

definitions.definition: To damage (the vehicle one is driving) in an accident; to have a minor collision with (another motor vehicle).
definitions.label_groups: transitive , chiefly Australia and New Zealand , UK , informal

main_definition: ( slang , dated ) To crash an aeroplane.
secondary_definitions: ( intransitive , chiefly Australia and New Zealand , UK , informal ) To crash ; to have an accident while controlling a vehicle.
( transitive , chiefly Australia and New Zealand , UK , informal ) To damage (the vehicle one is driving) in an accident; to have a minor collision with (another motor vehicle).
